data.description: Must See! Very spacious Sylvania home with over 2500 sqft! Hardwood Floor entry, Open concept kitchen, breakfast, family room with WB fireplace, perfect for guest gatherings and entertaining. Office upstairs overlooking the FR with a walk in attic/storage. Updates: New HWT 9/23, popcorn ceilings removed, New tub/shower enclosure & toilet in main bath (up), Master bath floor, New keyless entry back door, all in 2022. Remodeled 1/2 bath, Roof 6 yrs young. Large fenced backyard: hot tub, playset and shed stay. Guardian Alarm on home. 1 Year Amer Preferred Home Warranty Included ($499)!
